          "slidetitle": "AI in Research Today",
          "subtitle": "Shaping Modern Research With New Tools",
          "slidecontent": "• AI tools now widely used across literature review, data analysis, and academic writing\n• Adoption is rapid\n• Researchers increasingly rely on AI to process large datasets and identify patterns\n• These tools bring genuine efficiency gains, but also introduce new risks around accuracy and integrity\n• Some AI outputs can appear confident and credible even when factually wrong\n• Understanding both the benefits and the pitfalls is essential before using AI in any research context"
