          "slidetitle": "Spotting Fabricated AI Outputs",
          "subtitle": "Warning signs and verification strategies",
          "slidecontent": "• Citations that don't exist\n• Confident but wrong statistics\n• Vague, unverifiable sources\n• Suspiciously perfect results\n• Cross-check everything always"
